@startuml skills-architecture
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam sequenceParticipant underline

title Skills Architecture and Activation Flow

rectangle "Skills Repository\n(~/.copilot/skills/)" as Repo #LightBlue
note right of Repo #LightBlue
  Central hub for all skills.
  Managed with Git & CI/CD.
end note

rectangle "Skills Collection\n(architect, dev-workflow, etc.)" as Skills #LightGreen
note right of Skills #LightGreen
  Collection of specialized AI skills.
  Each provides tools, scripts, and docs.
end note

rectangle "OpenCode Platform\n(~/.config/opencode/skills/)" as OpenCode #LightYellow
note right of OpenCode #LightYellow
  Platform for loading and activating skills.
  Enables autonomous AI in conversations.
end note

rectangle "AI Conversation" as Conversation #LightCoral
note right of Conversation #LightCoral
  Interactive session where skills are used.
  AI responds with skill-enhanced behavior.
end note

Repo -[#Gray]-> Skills : contains
Skills -[#Blue]-> OpenCode : sync-skills.sh\n(deployment)
OpenCode -[#Red]-> Conversation : activate_all.py\n(execution)

note as Legend
  **Legend:**
  - Gray: Static relationships
  - Blue: Deployment/sync flow
  - Green: Reserved for future use
  - Red: AI conversation flow
end note

@enduml